613
00:38:34,965 --> 00:38:36,497
Thank you so much, Auntie.

614
00:38:36,508 --> 00:38:38,840
Take good care of yourself there.

615
00:38:38,851 --> 00:38:40,145
I’m worried about you.

616
00:38:40,379 --> 00:38:40,920
Alright.

617
00:38:40,943 --> 00:38:42,758
I’ll buy you Khanom La when I’m back.

618
00:38:44,600 --> 00:38:45,210
Thanks.

619
00:38:45,912 --> 00:38:48,911
By the way, isn’t Karan coming?

620
00:38:48,921 --> 00:38:50,342
I haven’t seen him today.

621
00:38:51,832 --> 00:38:53,291
He’s not coming.

622
00:38:54,509 --> 00:38:55,442
Of course, he’s coming.

623
00:38:55,802 --> 00:38:59,642
I see him park his car on the street next to our houses every night.

624
00:38:59,674 --> 00:39:01,751
He’s so handsome that I can’t mistake anyone else for him.

625
00:39:02,985 --> 00:39:04,241
Every night?

626
00:39:04,274 --> 00:39:04,946
Yes.

627
00:39:05,330 --> 00:39:09,648
Every night around 7-8 p.m.

628
00:39:10,066 --> 00:39:10,746
Wait.

629
00:39:12,011 --> 00:39:13,539
Didn’t he come to see you?

630
00:39:17,530 --> 00:39:18,648
7 p.m.?

631
00:39:19,580 --> 00:39:20,435
I’ll see you, friend.

632
00:39:20,445 --> 00:39:21,245
Bye-bye.

633
00:39:24,360 --> 00:39:24,942
Karan.

634
00:39:25,053 --> 00:39:25,663
Achi.

635
00:39:25,682 --> 00:39:26,746
Why are you in the car?

636
00:39:26,801 --> 00:39:29,148
I came down to get some stuff.

637
00:39:29,986 --> 00:39:32,448
Why can I hear the sound from your side too?

638
00:39:35,456 --> 00:39:37,056
Did Karan come to see me every night?

639
00:39:37,194 --> 00:39:39,056
Try opening your window.

640
00:39:41,684 --> 00:39:42,848
Thank you so much, Auntie.

641
00:39:44,290 --> 00:39:45,000
Alright.

642
00:39:45,657 --> 00:39:47,000
You’re welcome.

643
00:39:48,250 --> 00:39:49,493
I won’t keep you any longer.

644
00:39:49,505 --> 00:39:49,834
Okay.

645
00:39:49,847 --> 00:39:50,940
I should get going.

646
00:39:50,958 --> 00:39:51,782
I won’t keep you.

647
00:40:01,460 --> 00:40:02,542
(Hello, Achi.)

648
00:40:03,072 --> 00:40:03,939
Hello, Pai.

649
00:40:04,290 --> 00:40:05,016
Are you free?

650
00:40:05,057 --> 00:40:05,848
(Yes.)

651
00:40:06,128 --> 00:40:07,539
I need your help.

652
00:40:10,641 --> 00:40:11,842
Thank you so much for today.

653
00:40:12,128 --> 00:40:14,549
I’ll send you next month’s catalog as soon as I can.

654
00:40:15,894 --> 00:40:16,475
Rock.

655
00:40:16,496 --> 00:40:17,071
Duj.

656
00:40:17,327 --> 00:40:18,060
What are you guys doing here?

657
00:40:18,071 --> 00:40:18,888
We’re here to see you.

658
00:40:18,900 --> 00:40:19,801
Are we done here?

659
00:40:19,816 --> 00:40:20,814
Uh, yes.

660
00:40:20,949 --> 00:40:21,622
Thank you.

661
00:40:21,648 --> 00:40:22,782
- Where are we going?
- Bye.

662
00:40:22,826 --> 00:40:23,390
Rock.

663
00:40:23,405 --> 00:40:24,320
It’s nothing. We’re close.

664
00:40:24,334 --> 00:40:24,816
Very close.

665
00:40:24,820 --> 00:40:25,777
Where are we going?

666
00:40:25,795 --> 00:40:26,611
Bye.

667
00:40:26,884 --> 00:40:27,475
Rock.

668
00:40:27,522 --> 00:40:28,143
Hey.

669
00:40:35,087 --> 00:40:36,182
What’s going on, Rock?

670
00:40:36,367 --> 00:40:37,647
Why did you bring me here?

671
00:40:38,256 --> 00:40:38,918
I won’t tell you

672
00:40:38,927 --> 00:40:39,980
