673
00:40:41,050 --> 00:40:41,841
Don’t worry.

674
00:40:41,906 --> 00:40:43,543
Our job is done.

675
00:40:43,560 --> 00:40:44,782
You’ll find out soon.

676
00:40:45,774 --> 00:40:46,502
Let’s go.

677
00:40:55,204 --> 00:40:56,251
Liar!

678
00:40:58,822 --> 00:40:59,540
Achi.

679
00:41:01,080 --> 00:41:03,317
I thought you said no matter how much you missed me,

680
00:41:03,324 --> 00:41:05,013
you wouldn’t come to see me.

681
00:41:07,262 --> 00:41:10,177
But you secretly came to my house every day, didn’t you?

682
00:41:16,974 --> 00:41:17,628
You knew.

683
00:41:17,638 --> 00:41:19,777
How can I trust you now?

684
00:41:32,297 --> 00:41:33,642
I understand you though.

685
00:41:36,715 --> 00:41:39,819
I missed you so much that I couldn’t bear it either

686
00:41:41,198 --> 00:41:45,248
so I asked Duj and Rock to bring you here.

687
00:41:53,321 --> 00:41:56,186
I’m sorry I didn’t trust you before.

688
00:41:59,090 --> 00:42:01,952
Sometimes your love is so great

689
00:42:02,825 --> 00:42:06,137
that it’s hard to believe that someone could love me this much.

690
00:42:10,091 --> 00:42:11,536
But I trust you now.

691
00:42:14,317 --> 00:42:15,940
I trust you wholeheartedly.

692
00:42:20,053 --> 00:42:21,703
You don’t need to apologize.

693
00:42:23,445 --> 00:42:24,740
I’ve never been angry with you.

694
00:42:30,318 --> 00:42:33,254
In that case, can I ask you something?

695
00:42:37,054 --> 00:42:39,943
Are you sad that our first Loy Krathong plan failed?

696
00:42:42,037 --> 00:42:44,445
Apart from not wanting to make you feel uncomfortable,

697
00:42:45,872 --> 00:42:46,857
I’m sad

698
00:42:47,964 --> 00:42:50,780
but what can I do?

699
00:42:50,995 --> 00:42:53,180
It can’t be helped.

700
00:42:56,522 --> 00:42:58,019
Who says it can’t be helped?

701
00:43:08,616 --> 00:43:11,459
♪ ‘Cause you are extraordinary ♪

702
00:43:11,608 --> 00:43:14,002
♪ Turning days so ordinary ♪

703
00:43:14,014 --> 00:43:15,314
♪ Into something wonderful ♪

704
00:43:15,328 --> 00:43:19,305
♪ Every minute with you is so meaningful ♪

705
00:43:19,322 --> 00:43:22,259
♪ You give power so extraordinary ♪

706
00:43:22,290 --> 00:43:24,660
♪ To someone so ordinary ♪

707
00:43:24,680 --> 00:43:25,983
♪ Like me ♪

708
00:43:26,002 --> 00:43:29,964
♪ Never imagined my days would be like this ♪

709
00:43:29,991 --> 00:43:32,672
♪ With you, everything is magic ♪

710
00:43:33,631 --> 00:43:34,333
Achi.

711
00:43:34,432 --> 00:43:36,241
Let me do something for you for a change.

712
00:43:37,674 --> 00:43:43,140
At least I want to make our first Loy Krathong happen.

713
00:43:46,848 --> 00:43:48,245
What’s really going on?

714
00:43:48,482 --> 00:43:50,121
Did they come here to fight it out?

715
00:43:50,133 --> 00:43:51,654
You idiot.

716
00:43:52,472 --> 00:43:54,173
Look how romantic it is.

717
00:43:54,185 --> 00:43:55,669
Who would come here to fight?

718
00:43:55,685 --> 00:43:57,859
The couple came here to reconcile.

719
00:43:59,195 --> 00:44:00,154
Oh.

720
00:44:01,337 --> 00:44:02,154
No wonder.

721
00:44:03,351 --> 00:44:03,945
What?

722
00:44:04,734 --> 00:44:05,628
They’re a couple?

723
00:44:08,712 --> 00:44:09,447
Yes.

724
00:44:11,688 --> 00:44:12,499
Yes.

725
00:44:13,773 --> 00:44:14,882
You’ve been around them all this time.

726
00:44:14,896 --> 00:44:16,348
Haven’t you suspected anything?

727
00:44:17,007 --> 00:44:18,748
What could have been suspicious?

728
00:44:19,057 --> 00:44:20,779
They were just on a date at the mall.

729
00:44:21,382 --> 00:44:22,779
They slept over in each other’s homes.

730
00:44:23,842 --> 00:44:24,850
Exactly.

731
00:44:25,871 --> 00:44:27,379
What the f*ck?

732
00:44:27,764 --> 00:44:28,574
Keep it down.

733
00:44:29,200 --> 00:44:30,037
Keep it down.

734
00:44:30,047 --> 00:44:30,737
Shh!

735
00:44:42,118 --> 00:44:43,345
(What do you wish for?)

736
00:44:44,637 --> 00:44:47,248
(I wish we get to Loy Krathong together every year.)

737
00:44:48,542 --> 00:44:49,548
(What about you, Achi?)

738
00:44:50,598 --> 00:44:55,152
(I wish for our love to be strong.)

739
00:44:55,669 --> 00:44:57,182
(I wish nothing could destroy it.)

740
00:45:02,216 --> 00:45:03,841
You don’t have to make a wish for that.

741
00:45:04,425 --> 00:45:05,841
It’s up to us

742
00:45:07,776 --> 00:45:09,642
but I believe we can do it.

743
00:45:10,608 --> 00:45:12,340
No matter how far

744
00:45:12,866 --> 00:45:14,142
or for how long we are apart,

745
00:45:15,471 --> 00:45:17,059
I believe we’ll get through it.

746
00:45:21,168 --> 00:45:22,047
(Hello.)

747
00:45:22,146 --> 00:45:23,007
(We’re ready.)

748
00:45:23,029 --> 00:45:23,817
