756
00:46:38,472 --> 00:46:39,442
I’m not afraid.

757
00:46:40,402 --> 00:46:41,745
Whether you’re going to Nakhon,

758
00:46:42,268 --> 00:46:44,139
America,

759
00:46:44,472 --> 00:46:46,740
or Mars,

760
00:46:47,441 --> 00:46:49,642
my feelings for you will be the same.

761
00:46:50,383 --> 00:46:51,447
Nothing will change.

762
00:46:53,537 --> 00:46:56,742
So please focus on your work

763
00:46:56,934 --> 00:46:57,743
and don’t worry.

764
00:46:58,342 --> 00:46:59,644
I promise I’ll wait.

765
00:47:16,085 --> 00:47:17,351
(I love you, Achi.)

766
00:47:27,994 --> 00:47:29,253
I love you too, Karan.

767
00:47:53,128 --> 00:47:55,817
(Let this kiss take care of you for me.)

768
00:48:47,245 --> 00:48:48,330
Thank you so much.

769
00:48:48,351 --> 00:48:49,540
You’re the magical power

770
00:48:50,114 --> 00:48:51,582
that always reignites my passion.

771
00:48:53,201 --> 00:48:54,445
I want to ask

772
00:48:54,570 --> 00:48:56,650
if you’re open to seeing me.

773
00:48:57,810 --> 00:48:59,158
This is the new boss.

774
00:48:59,314 --> 00:49:00,266
Boss!

775
00:49:00,616 --> 00:49:03,047
I know everything seems hard on your first day.

776
00:49:03,400 --> 00:49:06,231
I think I have a lot to adjust to.

777
00:49:06,250 --> 00:49:07,546
You can do it for sure.

778
00:49:07,774 --> 00:49:09,146
A nice guy like you

779
00:49:09,414 --> 00:49:11,448
